00:38:48,940 --> 00:38:49,770
Why are you avoiding us?

932
00:38:51,090 --> 00:38:52,950
Imperial Preceptor talked to me just now.

933
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:54,050
He said

934
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:55,790
