959
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:33,500
That demon stole all of it

960
00:39:33,530 --> 00:39:34,130
last night.

961
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:35,610
I thought it was only

962
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:36,690
