963
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,930
But it turns out that it also likes balsams.

964
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:40,740
Get up.

965
00:39:43,870 --> 00:39:44,790
A while ago,

966
00:39:44,860 --> 00:39:45,620
His Majesty

967
00:39:45,640 --> 00:39:46,970
