968
00:39:47,310 --> 00:39:48,650
All the concubines were anxious about it.

969
00:39:49,170 --> 00:39:50,540
They tried their best

970
00:39:50,560 --> 00:39:51,530
to please the king

971
00:39:51,620 --> 00:39:53,370
