1037
00:42:24,100 --> 00:42:25,200
All our effort…

1038
00:42:30,740 --> 00:42:32,130
I see.

1039
00:42:33,900 --> 00:42:34,870
I'm so shocked

1040
00:42:35,110 --> 00:42:37,180
