1063
00:43:14,170 --> 00:43:15,020
The trick we used

1064
00:43:15,050 --> 00:43:15,880
won't work again.

1065
00:43:16,060 --> 00:43:17,210
But we can try something

1066
00:43:17,240 --> 00:43:17,920
